{"vv70:0.1":"Vimanavatthu ","vv70:0.2":"Purisavimana ","vv70:0.3":"Payasivagga ","vv70:0.4":"6. Bhikkhadayakavimanavatthu ","vv70:1.1":"“Uccamidam manithunam vimanam, ","vv70:1.2":"Samantato dvadasa yojanani; ","vv70:1.3":"Kutagara sattasata ulara, ","vv70:1.4":"Veluriyathambha rucakatthata subha. ","vv70:2.1":"Deviddhipattosi mahanubhavo, ","vv70:2.2":"Manussabhuto kimakasi punnam; ","vv70:2.3":"Kenasi evam jalitanubhavo, ","vv70:2.4":"Vanno ca te sabbadisa pabhasati”ti. ","vv70:3.1":"So devaputto attamano, ","vv70:3.2":"…pe… ","vv70:3.3":"yassa kammassidam phalam. ","vv70:4.1":"“Aham manussesu manussabhuto, ","vv70:4.2":"Disvana bhikkhum tasitam kilantam; ","vv70:4.3":"Ekaham bhikkham patipadayissam, ","vv70:4.4":"Samangi bhattena tada akasim. ","vv70:5.1":"Tena metadiso vanno, ","vv70:5.2":"…pe… ","vv70:5.3":"Vanno ca me sabbadisa pabhasati”ti. ","vv70:6.1":"Bhikkhadayakavimanam chattham. "}